        "text": ", and ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 18:24",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ff.—Considering the way in which Ap. had been made a rival to P. in Cor[2668], it shows magnanimity on Paul’s side to desire his return, and a modest delicacy on the side of Apollos to decline the request: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "καὶ πάντως οὐκ ἦν θέλημα ἵνα κ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "τ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "λ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "., “And there was no will at all (it was altogether contrary to his will) that he should come now”.—",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "εὐκαιρέω",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (see parls.) denotes “to have good opportunity”. The present ferment at Cor[2669] affords no ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "καιρὸς",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " for Apollos’ coming. For ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "πάντως",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "θέλημα ἵνα",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", see parls.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
